hadiths[105]{hadithnumber,text}:
7130,"Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jannat nagawar maamlon mein ghiri hui hai aur dozakh khaahishaate-nafsani mein ghiri hui hai."
7131,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki manind (tarah) riwayat ki.
7132,"Sufiyan ne abu Zinad se, unhon-ne Aaraj se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne irshad farmaya : maine apne nek bandon ke liye wo kuchh taiyaar kar rakha hai jisey na kisi aankh ne dekha hai na kisi kaan ne suna hai aur na kisi insan ke dil mein unka khayal tak guzra hai. kitabullah mein iska misdaaq (ye aayat ( hai : kisi ko malum nahi ke jo nek kaam kartey rahe unki jazaa ke taur par unki aankhon ko thanda karne ke liye kya kuchh chipa kar rakha gaya hai."
7133,"Malik ne abu Zinad se, unhon-ne Aaraj se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne irshad farmaya : maine apne nek bandon ke liye wo kuchh taiyaar karke jama kar rakha hai jo na kisi aankh ne dekha na kisi kaan ne suna aur na kisi insan ke dil mein un (ke tasawwur) ka guzar hua. (ye ( un (ne'maton ke) ilawa hai jinke ilawa hai. jinke barey main tumhen Allah Taala ne muttala kar diya hai."
7134,"Abu-Saleh ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : izzat aur jalaal waala Allah irshad farmata hai : maine apne nek bandon ke liye wo nematein taiyaar karkey jama ki hain jinko na kisi aankh ne dekha na kisi kaan ne suna aur na unka kisi insan ke dil mein khayal guzra, un nematon ke ilawa jin par Allah Taala ne tumhen muttala kar diya hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (ye aayat) padhi : kisi ko malum nahi ke unki aankhon ki thandak ke liye kya kuchh chipa kar rakha gaya hai."
7135,abu-Hazim ne kaha : maine Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ko bayan kartey huey suna : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik majlis mein hazir hua jis mein aap ne jannat ki sifat bayan ki yahan tak ke aap ne baat khatm ki. phir apni baat ke aakhir mein farmaya is ( jannat ( mein wo kuchh hai jo na kisi aankh ne dekha na kisi kaan ne suna na kisi insan ke dil mein iska khayal guzra . phir aap ne ye aayat padhi : unke pahlu bistaron se door rahtey hain wo khof ke aalim mein aur poori ummeed ke sath apne rab ko pukaartey hain aur ham ne jo rizq unko diya hai is mein se (Allah ki raah mein) kharch kartey hain. to koi zi hayaat (insan) nahi janta ke jo wo kartey hain uske siley mein unki aankhon ki thandak ke liye kya ( kuchh ( chipa kar rakha gaya hai.
7136,"abu-Saeed Maqbari ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : jannat mein aik darakht hai jiske saaey mein aik oont sawar sau saal tak chalta rahega."
7137,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki aur mazeed kaha : wo us (ke saaey) ko tay nahi kar sakega."
7138,"abu-Hazim ne Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : jannat mein aik darakht hai, aik sawar uske saaey mein sau saal tak chalta rahe to bhi usko tay na kar sakey."
7139,"abu-Hazim ne kaha : maine ye hadis Nauman bin abi Ayash zarqi ko sunai to unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kartey huey bayan kya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jannat mein aik darakht hai (jiske saaey mein) aik tez raftaar chharere ghodey par Sawar shakhs 100 saal chaley to bhi usey qata na kar sakey."
7140,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : izzat aur jalaal waala Allah ahle-jannat se farmaeyga : aey ahle-jannat! wo kahengey : labbaik, aey hamarey rab! zahe-naseeb ke terey samney hazir hain aur bhalai terey hathon mein hai chunanche wo farmaeyga : kya tum razi ho gaey ho? wo sab kahengey : ham razi kyon na hon? aey hamarey rab! jabke tuney hamein wo kuchh ata kar diya hai jo tuney apni saari makhlooq mein se kisi ko ata nahi farmaya, wo farmaeyga : kya main tumhen us se bhi behtar ata na karun? to wo kahengey : aey rab! (jooton ne ata kar diya hai) us se afzal kya hai? wo farmaeyga : main tum par apni raza nazil karta hun, iske baad main tum se kabhi naraz na hunga."
7141,"Yaqoob bin Abdur-Rehman qaari ne hamein abu-Hazim se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jannat waley jannat ke bula khaney ko is tarah dekhengey jis tarah tum log aasman mein sitaarey ko dekhtey ho."
7142,abu-Hazim ne kaha : maine ye riwayat Nauman bin abi Ayash se bayan ki to unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna : jis tarah tum aasman ke mashriqi ya maghribi ufuq mein chamaktey huey sitaarey ko dekhtey ho
7143,Wuhaib ne abu-Hazim se guzishta donon sanadon ke sath Yaqoob ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya.
7144,"Ata-bin-Yasar ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ahle-jannat fazeelat mein baahami farq ki bina par apne uper bula khaanon mein rehney walon ko is tarah dekhengey jis tarah tum aasman ke mashriqi ya maghribi kinarey mein chamaktey huey tanha sitaarey ko dekhtey ho. unhon (sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ( ne kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kya wo anbiya (Alaihissalam) ke rehney ki jaghein hongi jin tak doosra koi nahi pahunch sakta ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kyon nahi, us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! ye aisey mard hongey jo Allah Taala par eman laey aur unhon-ne rasulon ki tasdeeq ki."
7145,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : meri ummat mein mere sath sabse zyada mohabbat karne walon mein wo log (bhi) hain jo mere baad hongey, unmein se (har) aik ye chahta hoga ke kash! apne ahal w ayaal aur maal ki qurbani de kar mujhey dekh ley."
7146,"Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jannat mein aik bazar hai jis mein wo (ahle-jannat) har Juma ko aaya karengey to (us roz) shimaal ki aisi hua chalegi jo unke chehron par aur unke kapdon par phail jaeygi, wo husn aur zeenat mein aur badh jaeynge, wo apne ghar walon ke paas wapas aaeyngey to wo (bhi) husn w jamaal mein aur badh gaey hongey, unke ghar waley unse kahengey: Allah ki qasam! hamarey (yahaan se janey ke) baad tumhara husn w jamaal aur badh gaya hai. wo kahengey aur tum bhi, Allah ki qasam! hamarey peechhey tum log bhi aur zyada khoobsurat Husain ho gaey ho."
7147,"Ismail bin-Ulaih ne kaha : hamein Ayub ne Muhammad (bin Sirin) se khabar di ke (husoole-ilm ke liye jama hone-waale mardon aur aurton ne) aapsi izhar, tafaakhur ya ilmi muzaakra kartey huey (is mozu par) baat ki ke jannat mein mard zyada hongey ya auratein? to Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : kya abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya na tha : pehli jamat jo jannat mein dakhil hogi unki sooratein chaudahwin raat ke chaand jaisi hongi aur jo unke baad jaeygi wo aasman mein sabse zyada chamaktey huey sitaarey ki tarah hogi. unmein se har aadmi ki 2-2 beeviyan hongi (aisey shaffaaf aur munawwar jism waaliyan) unki pindliyon ka gooda gosht ke peechhey se nazar aayega. (poori) jannat mein biwi se mehroom koi shakhs bhi na hoga."
7148,"Sufiyan ne Ayub se aur unhon-ne (Muhammad) Ibne-Sirin se riwayat ki, kaha : mardon aur aurton mein bahas ho gaee ke unmein se jannat mein zyada kon hoga? phir unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se iske mutaalliq sawal kya to unhon-ne kaha : abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, (aagey) ibne-Ulaih ki hadis ki tarah."
7149,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha hamein abdul-Wahid bin Ziyad ne Ammara-bin-Qaqa se hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, kehtey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : pehlaa giroh jo jannat mein dakhil hoga. isi tarah hamein Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur Zuhair-bin-Harab ne hadis bayan ki. alfaz Quteba ke hain. donon ne kaha : hamein Jarir ne Umara se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : pehli jamat jo jannat mein dakhil hogi wo chaudahwin ke chaand ki shakl mein hongey. jo unke ( fauran ( baad jaenge wo aasman mein sabse zyada roshan chamaktey huey sitaarey ki shakl mein hongey, unhein peshab ki haajat hogi na pakhaney ki, na thookengey, na naak sinkengey, unki kanghiyaan soney ki hongi, paseena kastoori ka hoga, unki angeethiyon mein muattar ood (sulagta) hoga, unki beeviyan ghazaal chashm hoorein hongi , un sab ke akhlaq w aadaat aik hi aadmi ke khalq ke mutabiq hongey. apne walid Adam (Alaihissalam) ki shakl par, (qaamat mein) aasman ki taraf uthey huey sath hath ke barabar."
7150,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur abu-Kuraib ne hamein hadis bayan ki, donon ne kaha : hamein abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : meri ummat mein se pehla giroh jo jannat mein dakhil hoga wo chaudahwin raat ke chaand ki sura par hoga, jo unke baad hongey wo aasman mein intihai chamakdar sitaarey ki tarah hongey, phir wo tadreejan apne apney martabey ke mutabiq hongey, wo paakhaana karengey na peshaab, naak sinkengey na thookengey, unki kanghiyaan soney ki, angeethiyan muattar ood ki aur paseena kastoori ka hoga. un sab ke akhlaq aik hi insan ke (khoobsurat) akhlaq par (gaey) hongey, apne walid Hazrat Adam (Alaihissalam) ki qaamat par sath hath ( lambey ( hongey. ibne-Abi-Sheba ne kaha : aik hi aadmi ke akhlaq par, aur abu-Kuraib ne kaha : aik hi aadmi ki khilqat ( shakl w sura qadoqaamat ( par hongey aur ibne-Abi-Sheba ne kaha : apne walid (Hazrat Adam (Alaihissalam) ( ki shakl par hongey."
7151,"Mamar ne hamein Hammam-bin-Munabba se hadis bayan ki, kaha : ye hadisein hain jo Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kin, unhon-ne bahut si hadisein bayan kin, unmein se aik ye hai. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : pehla giroh jo jannat ke andar jaeyga, unki sooratein chaudahwin raat ke chaand ki sura par hongi. wo us (jannat) mein na thookengey, na naak sinkengey, na peshab paakhaana karengey. unke bartan aur unki kanghiyaan soney aur chandi ki hongi, unki angeethiyon mein ood muattar sulgega, unka paseena mushk ka hoga. unmein se har aik ki do-do beeviyan hongi , husn ke marey unki pindliyon ka gooda gosht se peechhey se dikhai dega. unke darmyan na kisi qism ka koi ikhtilaf hoga, na baahami bughz hoga. un sab ke dil aik dil (ki tarah) hongey. wo subah w Sham apne Allah ki tasbeeh kartey hongey."
7152,"Jarir ne Aamash se, unhon-ne abu Sufiyan se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna, ahle-jannat wahan khaaengey piyengey. lekin na usmein thookengey na peshab karengey, na rafa haajat (peshab-pakhaney se farigh honey) karengey aur na naak sinkengey. unhon ( sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ( ne puchha : phir unke khaney ka kya banega. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik dakaar (aaeygi) aur kastoori ke pasiney ki tarah paseena aayega. unko tasbeeh aur hamd (ke naghmey) isi tarah (fitrat ke andar) ilhaam kar diye jaeynge jis tarah saans ko ilhaam (karke unki fitrat mein shamil) kar diya jata hai."
7153,abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke farman : mushk ke pasiney ki tarah tak riwayat ki.
7154,"Hasan-bin-Ali Hulwani aur Hajjaj-bin shaair donon ne mujhey abu-Aasim se riwayat ki. Hasan ne kaha : hamein abu-Aasim ne hadis bayan ki kaha : ibne-Juraij se riwayat hai unhon-ne kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir bin Aabdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ahle-jannat usmein khaaein aur piengey. ( lekin) wo usmein rafa haajat (peshab-pakhana) karengey, na naak sinkengey, na peshab karengey albatta unka khana dakaar (ki shakl mein tahleel (ho jaeyga jo mushk ki tarah khushbudaar hogi. unhein ( khud b-khud ( Allah ki pakeezgi aur uski hamd karna ilhaam kya jaeyga jis tarah unhein ( khud b-khud ( saans lena ilhaam kya gaya hai. kaha : aur Hajjaj ki hadis mein hai : unki asl ghizaa yahi hogi."
7155,"Yahya ne kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne hadis bayan ki kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ( hadis) riwayat ki magar unhon-ne kaha : aur unhein tasbeeh w takbeer isi tarah ilhaam ki jaeygi jis tarah saans lena ilhaam kya jata hai."
7156,abu Raafe ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs jannat mein dakhil hoga wo naaz w nam mein hoga kabhi tang haal na hoga. uska libaas puraana hoga na uski jawaani dhalegi.
7157,"Sory ne kaha : mujhey Abu-Ishaq ne hadis bayan ki, (abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam) Agharr (bin-Abdullah) ne unhein Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri aur Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik elaan karne wala eilaan karega. yaqinan tumharey liye ye (inaam bhi) hai ke tum hamesha sihatmand rahogey. kabhi bimar na padogey, aur ye bhi tumharey liye hai ke zinda rahogey. kabhi maut ka shikar nahi hogey aur ye bhi tumharey liye hai ke jawan rahogey. kabhi boodhey na hogey aur ye bhi tumharey liye hai ke hamesha naaz w nam mein rahogey. kabhi zahmat na dekhogey. yahi izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ka farman (waazeh karta) hai : aur unhein awaz dekar kaha jaeyga ke yahi tumhari jannat hai jiske tum un aamaal ki wjah se se jo tum kartey rahe waaris bana diye gaey ho."
7158,"abu Qudama Haris bin Ubaid ne abu-Imran Jawni se, unhon-ne Abu-Bakar bin-Abdullah-bin Qais se, unhon-ne apne walid (abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu)) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : momin ke liye jannat mein aik khema hoga. jo aik poley chamaktey safaid moti ka bana hua hoga. uski lambai 70 meel hogi. us ( khemey) mein momin ke bahut se ghar waley hongey. wo (baari-baari) unke yahan chakkar lagaega. (lekin) wo (is qadr faasley pe hongey ke) aik doosrey ko nahi dekhtey hongey. (kisi ka bhi dil pareshani ya hasad ka shikar na hoga.)"
7159,abu Abdus-Samad ne kaha : hamein abu-Imran Jawni ne Abu-Bakar bin-Abdullah-bin Qais se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jannat mein thothey chamakdaar safaid moti ka khema hoga. uski chaudai sath meel hogi. uske har koney mein ghar waley hongey wo aik doosrey ko nahi dekhtey hongey. momin unke yahan chakkar lagaya karega.
7160,"Hammam ne abu-Imran jawni se khabar di unhon-ne Abu-Bakar-bin-abu-Musa-bin-Qais se unhon-ne apne walid (abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu)) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : khema aik moti (ka) hoga uper ki taraf uski lambai ( bulandi ( sath (60) meel hogi. iske har koney mein momin ke ghar waley hongey, wo dusron ko nahi dekhengey."
7161,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : saihaan, jeehaan, Furaat aur neel sab jannat ki (taraf se aaney wal ( nehrein hain."
7162,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : jannat mein aisi qaumein (ummatein, jamatein) dakhil hongi jinke dil parindon ke dilon ki tarah hongey."
7163,"Hammam-bin-Munabba se riwayat hai unhon-ne kaha : ye wo hadisein hain jo hamein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan ki unmein se (eik ( ye hai ke aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne Hazrat Adam (Alaihissalam) ko apni (pasandida) sura par paida farmaya, unka qad sath hath tha jab unko takhleeq farma (bana) liya to farmaya : jayen aur us ( samney wali) jamat ko salam kahin aur wo farishton ki jamat hai jo baithey huey hain aur jis tarah wo aapko salam kahin usey ghaur se sunein , wahi aap ka aur aap ki aulad ka salam hoga. farmaya wo gaey aur kaha : (السلام عليك) unhon-ne (jawab mein) kaha :          (السلام عليك ورحمة الله) farmaya : unhon-ne un ( Adam (Alaihissalam) (ke liye ( ورحمة الله (ka izafa kiya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : har wo shakhs jo jannat mein dakhil hoga Adam (Alaihissalam) ki (usi ( sura par hoga aur unki qaamat (qad) ( jannat mein) sath hath thi phir unke baad aaj tak (unki aulad ki) khilqat chhoti hoti rahi hai."
7164,"Hazrat Abdullah (bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is (qiyamat ke) roz jahannam ko laya jaeyga, uski sattar (70) hazaar lagaamein hongi, har lagaam ke sath sattar (70) hazaar Farishtey hongey jo usey kheench rahe hongey."
7165,"abu Zinad ne Aaraj se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tumhari ye aag . jis ko ibne-Aadam roshan karta hai. jahannam ki garmi ke sattar (70) hisson mein se aik hissey (ki haraarat) ke barabar hai. unhon (sahaba) ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! Allah ki qism ! ye aag bhi to kafi thi, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey unhattar hissey zyada rakha gaya hai, har hissey is (duniya ki aag) ki tarah garm hai."
7166,"Mamar ne hamein Hammam-bin-Munabba se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se abu-Zinad ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki, magar unhon ( Mamar ( ne kaha : wo sab ke sab us jaisi haraarat rakhtey hain."
7167,"Khalaf-bin-khaleefa ne kaha : hamein Yazeed-bin-kaisaan ne abu-Hazim se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they ke aap ne kisi bahut wazni cheez ke girney ki awaz suni. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tum jantey ho ye kaisi awaz thi? kaha : ham ne kaha : Allah aur uska rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) zyada jaanney waley hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye aik patthar tha jis ko sattar (70) saal pahley jahannam mein phainkaa gaya tha, ye ab usmein gira hai, yahan tak ke uski gehrai tak pahunch gaya hai."
7168,"Marwan ne hamein Yazeed-bin-kaisaan se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Hazim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur kaha : ye  (ab) iske nichley hissey mein gira hai aur tum ne iske girney ki awaz suni hai."
7169,"Sheban bin Abdur-Rehman ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : Qatada ne kaha : maine abu-Nazara ko Hazrat Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kartey huey suna, unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : un ( jahannamiyon ( mein se koi aisa hoga jiske takhnon tak aag lipti hogi aur koi aisa hoga jiski kamar tak lipti hogi aur koi aisa hoga jiski gardan tak lipti hogi."
7170,"abdul-wahaab-bin-Ata ne hamein Saeed se khabar di, unhon-ne Qatada se riwayat ki, kaha : maine abu-Nazara ko suna, wo Hazrat Samra-bin-Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey they ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : unmein se koi aisa hoga jiske donon takhnon tak aag lipti hogi, unmein se koi aisa hoga jinke donon ghutnon tak aag lipti hogi aur koi aisa hoga jiski kamar tak aag lipti hogi aur koi aisa hoga jiski hansli ki haddi tak aag pakdey gi."
7171,Rooh ne kaha : hamein Saeed ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne (kamar par izaar baandhney ki jagah ke liye) (hujaztihee) ke bajaey (hiqwaih) ka lafz istemal kiya.
7172,"Sufiyan ne abu-Zinad se, unhon-ne Aaraj se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : dozakh aur jannat mein mubaahasa (bahas) hua to us (dozakh) ne kaha : mere andar jabbaar aur mutakabbir dakhil hongey aur us (jannat) ne kaha : mere andar (asbaab duniya ke eitibaar se) zaeef aur miskeen log dakhil hongey. izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne us (dozakh) se kaha : tum mera azab ho, tumharey zariey se main jinhein chaahoon ga azab doonga. ya shayad farmaya : jinhein chaahoon ga mubtala karunga aur us (jannat  se kaha : to meri rehmat hai aur tumharey zariey se jis par chaahoon ga raham karunga aur tum donon ke liye wo miqdar hogi jo usko bhar degi."
7173,"Warqa ne mujhey abu Zinad se, unhon-ne Aaraj se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : dozakh aur jannat ne aapasi (apni-apni bartari ke) dalaayel diye. dozakh ne kaha : mujhey jabr aur takabbur karne walon (ka thikana honey) ki bina par tarjeeh hasil hai. jannat ne kaha : mujhey kya hua hai ke mere andar kamzor, khaak nasheen, aur aajiz aur laachaar log hi dakhil hongey? izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne jannat se farmaya : to meri rehmat hai main apne bandon mein se jin par chaahoon ga terey zariey se rehmat karunga aur dozakh se kaha : to mera azab hai main apne bandon mein se jis ko chaahoon ga tumharey zariey se azab doonga aur tum donon ke liye itni (makhlooq)  hai jis se tum bhar jao. rahi aag to wo poori tarah se nahi bharey gi chunanche wo (Allah) iske uper apna qadam rakhega to wo kahegi ! bas-bas ! us waqt wo bhar jaeygi aur aapas mein simat jaeygi."
7174,Ayub ne Ibne-Sirin se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jannat aur dozakh ne (apni-apni bartari ke) dalaayel diye. phir abu Zinad ki hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan ki.
7175,"Mamar ne hamein Hammam-bin-Munabba se hadis bayan ki, kaha : ye hadisein hain jo Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kin, unhon-ne bahut si hadisein bayan kin, unmein se (eik) ye hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jannat aur dozakh ne (apne-apney barey mein) aik doosrey ko dalaayel diye. dozakh ne kaha : mujhey takabbur aur jabr karne walon (ka thikana honey) ki bina par tarjeeh hasil hai. jannat ne kaha : mera kya haal hai ke mere andar logon mein se kamzor, khaak nasheen aur seedhey, saadey log dakhil hongey? to izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne jannat se farmaya : to saraasar meri rehmat hai, terey zariey se main apne bandon mein se jis ko chaahoon ga rehmat se nawaazon ga. aur dozakh se kaha : to sirf aur sirf mera azab hai, terey zariey se main apne bandon mein se jis ko chaahoon ga azab mein daalun ga aur tum donon mein se har aik ke liye itney bandey hain jin se wo bhar jaey. jahan tak aag ka talluq hai to wo nahi bharey gi. yahan tak ke Allah tabarak w taala apna qadam (us par) rakh dega to wo kahegi bas, bas, bas us waqt wo bhar jaeygi, iske kuchh hissey kuchh ke sath simat jaengey. Allah Taala apni makhlooq mein se kisi par zulm nahi karega aur jahan tak jannat ka talluq hai to Allah (iske liye) aik makhlooq taiyaar kar dega."
7176,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jannat aur dozakh ne aik doosrey ke samney dalaayel diye. phir unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis ki tarah Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke us farman : tum donon ko bharnaa meri zimme-dari hai tak bayan kiya aur uske baad ke mazeed alfaz zikr nahi kiye."
7177,"Sheban ne hamein Qatada se hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : dozakh musalsal yahi kehti rahegi : kya aur zyada hai? yahan tak ke rabbul-izzat tabarak w taala usmein apna qadam tikaaey ga to wo kahegi bas-bas teri izzat ki qism ! (mera mutalba khatm ho gaya). aur iska aik hissey doosrey hissey se simat jaeyga."
7178,"Abaan-bin-Yazeed attaar ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Qatada ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Sheban ki hadis ke ham mana riwayat ki."
7179,"abdul-wahaab-bin-Ata ne hamein us (Allah) Shaanwaley ke is farman : jis din ham jahannam se kahein gey ke kya to bhar gaee aur wo kahegi : kya aur zyada hai? ke barey mein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne hamein Saeed se khabar di, unhon-ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jahannam mein musalsal (logon ko) daala jata rahega aur wo kehti rahegi : kya aur hai? yahan tak ke rabbul-izzat usmein apna paon rakh dega. to uska kuchh, kuchh ki taraf simat jaeyga aur wo kahegi : teri izzat aur terey karam ki qism ! bas-bas aur jannat mein musalsal gunjaaish rahegi yahan tak ke Allah Taala uske liye aik khilqat (makhlooq) paida kar dega aur unhein jannat ki bachi hui jagah mein basaa dega."
7180,"Sabit ne kaha : maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jannat mein se jis hissey ke barey mein Allah Taala chaahega ke baqi bach jaey wo baqi bach jaeyga, phir Allah Taala iske liye, jahan se chaahega , makhlooq paida kar dega."
7181,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur abu-Kuraib ne hamein hadis bayan ki. donon ke alfaz miltey-jultey hain. donon ne kaha : hamein abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se hadis bayan ki. unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat ke din maut ko is tarah laya jaeyga jaisey wo siyah aur safaid mendha ho. abu-Kuraib ne mazeed ye kaha, chunanche usey jannat aur jahannam ke darmyan mein khada kar diya jaeyga baqi bachi hadis (ke alfaz ( mein donon muttafiq hain. to (elaan karne wala pukar kar) kahega : aey jannat waalo ! kya usey pehchantey ho? to wo jhaankein gey , dekhengey aur kahengey : haan. ye maut hai. farmaya : phir kaha jaeyga : aey jahannam waalo ! kya usey pehchantey ho? to wo jhaankein gey , dekhengey aur kahengey , haan , ye maut hai. farmaya : phir uske barey mein hukm diya jaeyga aur usey zabah kar diya jaeyga farmaya : phir kaha jaeyga : aey jannat waalo ! (ab) dawaam (hameshgi) hi dawaam hai maut nahi hai aur aey jahannam waalo ! (ab) dawaam hi dawaam hai, maut nahi hai. kaha : phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (ye aayat ( padhi :                                                                                                                              ''unko hasarat ke din se daraaiye jab mamla niptaa diya jaeyga aur wo saraasar ghafalat mein hain aur wo imaan nahi latey aur aap ne apne hath se duniya ki taraf ishara farmaya.''"
7182,"hamein Jarir ne Aamash se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se, aur unhon-ne Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab jannat waley jannat mein aur jahannam waley jahannam mein dakhil kar diye jaengey. to kaha jaeyga aey ahle-jannat ! iske baad abu-Muawiya ki hadis ke ham mana bayan kiya, magar unhon-ne kaha : yahi (usi ke mutabiq) hai us (Allah) Shanwaley ka farman aur unhon-ne nahi kaha, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (ye aayat ( padhi aur (usi tarah) unhon-ne ye bhi zikr nahi kiya ke aap ne apne hath se duniyaa ki taraf ishara farmaya."
7183,"Naafe ne hamein hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Abdullah ( ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ahle-jannat ko jannat mein dakhil karega aur ahale-jahannam ko jahannam mein dakhil karega. phir unke darmyan aik elaan karne wala khada ho kar elaan karega : aey ahle-jannat ! ab maut nahi hai, aur aey ahale-dozakh ! ab maut nahi hai har shakhs jahan hai wahin hamesha rehney wala hai."
7184,ibne- Wahab ne kaha : mujhey Umar-bin-Muhammad-bin-Zaid-bin-Abdullah-bin-Umar-bin-Khattab ne hadis bayan ki ke unhein unke walid ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab jannat waley jannat mein aur jahannam waley jahannam mein chaley jaeinge to maut ko zabah kiya jaeyga aur usko jannat aur dozakh ke darmyan khada kiya jaeyga phir usey zabah kar diya jaeyga. phir elaan karne wala elaan karega : aey jannat waalo ! (ab) maut nahi hai (aur) aey jahannam waalo ! (ab) maut nahi hai. ahle-jannat ko apni khushi par mazeed khushi hasil ho jaeygi aur jahannam walon ko apne gham par mazeed gham laahiq hoga.
7185,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kaafir ki daadh ya ( farmaya :) kaafir ka kuchli daant Uhud pahaad jitna ho jaeyga aur uski khaal ki motaai teen din chalney ki masafat (doori) ke barabar hogi."
7186,"abu-Kuraib aur Ahmed-bin-Umar-wakee ne hamein hadis bayan ki, donon ne kaha : hamein ibne- Fuzel ne apne walid se, unhon-ne abu-Hazim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne usey marfoo bayan kartey huey kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jahannam mein kaafir ke do kandhon ke darmyan tez raftaar sawar ki teen din ki masafat (doori) ke barabar fasla hoga. wakee ne jahannam mein ke alfaz bayan nahi kiye."
7187,"Muaz Anbari ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Ma'bad-bin-Khalid ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Haarisa-bin-Wahab (Raziallahu anhu) se suna ke unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya main tumhen ahle-jannat ke barey mein khabar na dun? unhon ( sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ( ne kaha : kyon nahi ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : har kamzor jisey kamzor samjha jata hai. (magar aisa ke) agar (kisi mamley mein) Allah par qism kha ley to wo uski qism poori kar de. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ! kya main tumhen ahale-jahannam ke barey mein khabar na dun? logon ne kaha : kyon nahi ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : har ujadd , maal ikattha karne wala, usey kharch na karne wala aur takabbur ikhtiyar karne wala."
7188,Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki magar usmein kaha : kya main tumhari rehnumai na karun?
7189,"Sufiyan ne hamein Mabad-bin-Khalid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Haarisa-bin-Wahab Khuzai (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya main tumhen ahle-jannat ki khabar na dun? har kamzor jisey kamzor aur laachaar samjha jata hai. (lekin aisa ke) agar Allah par (aitimaad kartey huey) qism kha ley to wo usey poori kar de. kya main tumhen ahale-jahannam ke barey mein khabar na dun? har maal sametney wala aur usey kharch na karne waalaa, bad asl , mutakabbir (takabbur karne wala)."
7190,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kabhi-kabhi bikhrey huey baalon wala jisey darwazey par se lota diya jata hai. (aisa hota hai) ke Allah par (aitimaad kartey huey) qism kha ley to wo ( Allah ( usey poori kar deta hai.
7191,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur abu-Kuraib ne hamein hadis bayan ki, donon ne kaha : hamein ibne-Numair ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Zama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khutba irshad farmaya to (hazrat Saleh (Alaihissalam) ki) ontni ka aur uski koonchein kaatney waley shakhs ka zikr farmaya, phir aap ne padha : jab us (qabeeley) ka badbakht tareen shakhs utha (aap ne farmaya : qabila Samood ka ( sabse taaqatwar, shar phailaaney waalaa, jis ko apni qaum ka pura tahaffuz hasil tha, jis tarah abu-Zama ( Aswad bin matlab ( hai, ( koonchein kaatney ke liye) utha . phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is silsiley mein aurton ka bhi zikr kya, ( sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ko) unke barey mein waz (nasihat) w nasihat farmai, phir farmaya : kya wjah hai ke tum mein se koi apni biwi ko (is tarah) kode se maarta hai Abu-Bakar ki riwayat mein hai : jis tarah londi ko maarta hai aur abu-Kuraib ki riwayat mein hai : jis tarah ghulam ko maarta hai. phir shayad din ke aakhir mein usi ke sath ham bistari karega. phir un ( sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ( ko gooz par hansney ke barey mein nasihat farmai : tum mein se koi Kab tak us kaam par hansta rahega jisey wo khud karta hai."
7192,"Suhel ke walid ( Abu-Saleh ( ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine Urwa bin Luhyi bin Qama bin khandaf, un banu-Kab walon ke jadde-aala (poorvaj) ko dekha, wo jahannam main apni antadiyan ghaseet raha tha."
7193,"ibne-Shahab ne kaha : maine Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se suna, wo kehtey hain : Baheera wo janwar hai jiska doodh jhootey khudaaon ( buton (ke chadhaawey ke liye dohna band kar diya jata hai, isliye koi shakhs unko nahi dohtaa tha, aur saaiba wo janwar hai jisey jhootey khudaaon (ki sawari ke liye) khula chhod diya jata hai. is par koi cheez tak nahi laadi jati aur ibne-Musaiyab ne kaha : Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine Amr bin Aamir Khuzai ko dekha, wo jahannam main apni antadiyaan ghaseet raha tha, wo pehla shakhs tha jisne sabse pahley (buton ke naam par) khula chhoda janey wala janwar chhoda tha."
7194,"Suhel ke walid (Abu-Saleh) ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ahale-jahannam ki 2 qismein aisi hain jinko (duniyawi zindagi mein) maine ( khud ( nahi dekha. aik giroh wo hai jiske paas gaayon ki dumon ki tarah se kode hongey jin se wo logon ko maarengey aur (doosrey giroh mein) wo auratein hain jo libaas pahney huey (bhi) nangi hongi, dusron ko (gunah par) maail karne wali, khud maail honey wali hongi unke sar (ilaqa) bakht ki oontniyon ke aik taraf jhukey huey kohaanon jaisey hongey. ye auratein jannat mein dakhil hongi na uski khushbu soonghengi. halanke uski khushbu itney-itney (lambey) faasley se mehsus hoti hogi."
7195,"Zaid-bin-Hubab ne kaha : hamein Aflah bin Saeed ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke aazad karda ghulam Abdullah-bin Raafe ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qareeb hai ke agar tumhen lambi muddat mil gaee to tum aisey logon ko dekhogey jinke hath mein gaayon ki dumon jaisey (kode) hongey, wo Allah ke ghazab mein subah guzaarengey aur Allah ki sakht naaraazagi mein Sham Basar karengey."
7196,"abu-Aamir Aqdi ne kaha : hamein Aflah bin Saeed ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke aazad karda ghulam Abdullah-bin Raafe ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : agar tumhen lambi muddat mil gaee to qareeb hai ke tum aisey logon ko dekhogey jinki subah Allah ki sakht naaraazagi mein aur jinki Sham (Syria) Allah ki laanat ke saaey mein hogi. unke hathon mein gaayon ki damon ki tarah (kode) hongey."
7197,"Abdullah-bin-Idris , Muhammad-bin Numer , Muhammad-bin-Bishr, Musa bin Aa'yun aur abu-Usama aur Yahya-bin-Saeed sab ne hamein Ismail bin abi Khalid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Qais ne hadis sunai : unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Mustaurid (bin Shaddad qarshi) fahri (Raziallahu anhu) se suna : wo kehtey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah ki qasam! aakhirat (ke muqaabley) mein duniya ki haisiyat us se zyada nahi jis tarah tum mein se koi shakhs apni aik ungli samandar mein daley. Yahya ne apni angushte-shahadat ki taraf ishara kya. phir dekhey wo (ungli) usmein se kya (nikal kar) laati hai. Yahya (bin Saeed qattaan ki riwayat (ke ilawa baqi sab ki hadis main (saraahat se) ye alfaz hain maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna aur Hazrat mustaurid bin Shaddad fahri (Raziallahu anhu) se abu-Usama ki hadis mein bhi) yahi alfaz hain) aur unki hadis mein ye bhi hai ke) abu-Usama ne) aur Ismail (bin abi Khalid ( ne angoothey ke sath ishara kya."
7198,"Ummul-Momenin Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, maine suna Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they : ''qiyaamat ke din log hashr (Jama) kiye jaeinge nangey paon, nangey badan , bin khatna kiye huey. '' maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! mard aur aurat aik sath hongey to aik-doosrey ko dekhega. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : '' : aey Aaisha ! wahan ki museebat aisi sakht hogi ke koi doosrey ko na dekhega.'' (apni-apni fikr mein hongey) ."
7199,abu-Khalid Ahmar ne hamein Hatim bin abi sagheera se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne apni riwayat mein be khatna zikr nahi kya.
7200,"saiyedna Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne suna Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they khutbe mein : ''tum Allah se milogey paa-piyaada (paidal), nangey paon, nangey badan , bin khatna .'' ( jaisey paida huey they)."
7201,"Wakee aur Muaz donon ne hamein Shoba se hadis bayan ki, neez Muhammad-bin-Musanna aur Muhammad-bin Bishr ne. alfaz ibne- Musanna ke hain. kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne Shoba se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Mughira bin Nauman se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey darmyan nasihat aamoz khutba dene ke liye khadey huey aur farmaya : aey logo ! tum ko Allah ke samney nangey paon be libaas be khatna ikattha kya jaeyga ( Quran Majeed mein hai) : jis tarah ham ne pehli paidaaish ki shuruat ki thi usi ko dobara lotaaengey. ye ham par) pukhta ( wada hai ham yahi karne waley hain. yad rakho ! makhlooqat mein se sabse pahley jinhein libaas pahnaayaa jaeyga wo Ibrahim hongey aur yad rakho ! meri ummat mein se kuchh log laey jaeinge, phir unhein pakad kar baain (jahannam ki) taraf ley jaya jaeyga main kahunga. mere rab! mere sathi hain. to kaha jaeyga aapko malum nahi unhon-ne aap ke baad (deen mein) kya nai baatein nikaali thin. to wahi kuchh kahunga jo nek bandey (Eisaa (Alaihissalam) ( kahengey : main un par gawah tha jab tak mein unke darmyan raha jab tu ney mujhey utha liya to un par to nigahbaan tha. agar to unhein azab de to be-shak ye terey bandey hain aur agar to unhein bakhsh de to yaqinan tu hi bada ghalib aur bada daana hai. farmaya : to mujh se kaha jaeyga jab se aap unse juda huey they. ye musalsal apni eidiyon par lot-tey chaley gaey aur Wakee aur Muaz ki hadis mein hai : to kaha jaeyga aap nahi jantey ke unhon-ne aap ke baad) Deen mein) kya nai baatein nikaali thin."
7202,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : (qiyamat ke din) logon ko teen tariqon se ( Allah ke samney ( ikattha kya jaeyga ( kuchh log ( khof aur ummeed ke aalim mein hongey aur (wo log jinhein haziri ke waqt bhi izzat naseeb hogi. hasab maraatib) wo (afraad) aik oont par (sawar) hongey aur teen aik oont par aur char aik oont par aur das aik oont par (sawar hokar maidaane-hashr mein aaeingey) aur baqi sab logon ko aag (apne gherey mein) ikattha karke laeygi. jahan un par raat aaeygi, wo ( aag (raat ko bhi unke sath hogi, jahan unhein do-pahar hogi wo do-pahar ko bhi unke sath rukegi, wo jahan subah karengey wo subah ke waqt bhi unke sath hogi aur jahan wo log Sham karengey wo Sham ko bhi unke sath hogi."
7203,"Zuhair-bin-Harab Muhammad-bin-Musanna aur Ubaidullah bin Saeed ne hamein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Ubaidullah se hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (is aayat ki tafseer ( riwayat ki is din log rabbul-aalameen ke samney khadey hongey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : yahan tak ke unmein se koi is tarah khada hoga ke iska paseena iske kanon ke darmyan tak hoga aur ibne- Musanna ki riwayat mein hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( unmein se koi ke bajaey) farmaya : log khadey hongey. unhon-ne ( ibne- Musanna ( ne ( aayat mein) yaum (is din) ka zikr nahi kya."
7204,"Musa-bin-Aqba, Ibne-Aun, Imam Malik, Ayub aur Saleh sab ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi hadis ke ham mana riwayat bayan ki jo Ubaidullah ne Naafe se bayan ki hai albatta Musa-bin-Aqba aur Saleh ki riwayat hai : yahan tak ke unmein se koi shakhs aadhey kanon tak apne pasiney mein doobaa hoga."
7205,Abdul-Azeez-bin-Muhammad ne Saur se unhon-ne abul-gaees se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : yaqinan paseena qiyamat ke din zamin mein donon hathon ke phailaaw ke 70 guna faasley tak chala jaeyga aur logon ke munh ya unke kanon tak pahuncha hoga. Saur ko shak hai ke unhon (abul-gaees) ne donon mein se kon se alfaz kahey?
7206,"Abdur-Rehman-bin-Jaabir se riwayat hai kaha mujhey Sulaim-bin-Aamir ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Hazrat Miqdaad-bin-Aswad (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : qiyamat ke din suraj makhlooqat ke bahut nazdeek aa jaeyga yahan tak ke unse aik meel ke faasley par hoga. Sulai-bin-Aamir ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! mujhey malum nahi ke meel se un (miqdaad (Raziallahu anhu)) ki murad masafat (doori) hai ya wo silai jis se aankh mein surma daala jata hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : log apne aamal ke mutabiq pasiney mein (doobey) hongey unmein se koi apne donon takhnon tak koi apne donon ghutnon tak koi apne donon koolhon tak aur koi aisa hoga jisey pasiney ne lagaam daal rakhi hogi. (miqdaad (Raziallahu anhu)) kaha : aur (aisa farmatey huey) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hath se apne dahan (munh) Mubarak ki taraf ishara farmaya."
7207,"Abu-Ghassan Mismai Muhammad-bin-Musanna aur Muhammad-bin-Bashar-bin-Usman ne hamein hadis bayan ki. alfaz Abu-Ghassan aur ibne-Musanna ke hain donon ne kaha : Muaz-bin-Hisham ne hamein hadis bayan ki kaha : mujhey mere walid ne Qatada se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Mutarrif-bin-Abdullah-bin-Shikhkhir se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ayaaz-bin-himaar mujaashee (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne khutbey mein irshad farmaya : suno ! mere rab ne mujhey ye hukm diya hai ke main tumhen un baton ki taleem dun jo tumhen malum nahi aur Allah Taala ne aaj mujhey unka ilm ata kiya hai. ( Allah Taala ne farmaya hai) har maal jo maine kisi bandey ko ata kiya ( uski qismat mein likha ( halal hai aur maine apne tamam bandon ko) haq ke liye) yaksoo paida kiya phir shayatin unke paas aaey aur unhein unke Deen se door kheench liya aur jo maine unke liye halal kiya tha unhon-ne usey unke liye haram kar diya. aur un ( bandon ( ko hukm diya ke wo mere sath shirk karein jiske liye maine koi daleel nazil nahi ki thi aur Allah ne zamin walon ki taraf nazar farmai to ahle-kitab ke) kuchh ( bachey-khuchey logon ke siwa baqi Arab aur ajam sab par sakht naraz hua aur) mujh se) farmaya : maine aapko isliye maboos kiya (bheja) ke main aap ki aur aap ke zariey se dusron ki aazmaish karun aur maine aap par aik aisi kitab nazil ki hai jisey pani dho (kar mitaa) nahi sakta. aap sotey huey bhi uski tilawat karengey aur jaagtey huey bhi. aur Allah ne mujhey hukm diya ke main Quraish ko (unke ma'boodon aur un baap-dada aur ajdaad ke shirk aur gunahon par aar (sharm) dilaatey huey unhein) jalaaun. maine kaha : mere rab wo mere sar ko tukdey-tukdey karke roti ki tarah kar dengey. to (Allah ne) farmaya : aap unhein bahar nikaalein jis tarah unhon-ne aapko bahar nikala aur unse ladai karein. ham aapko ladwaaein gey aur) Allah ki raah mein) kharch karein aap par kharch kiya jaeyga aur aap lashkar bhejiin ham us jaisey panch lashkar bhejein gey aur jo log aap ke farman bardaar hain unke zariey se naafarmaanon ke khilaf jang karein. (phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne) farmaya : ahle-jannat teen ( tarah ke log ( hain aisa saltanat wala jo aadil hai. sadqa karne wala hai usey achchhai ki taufeeq di gaee hai. aur aisa meharban shakhs jo har qaraabat daar aur har musalman ke liye narm dil hai aur wo iffat shiaar ( buraaiyon se bach kar chalney wala ( jo ayaal daar hai, ( phir bhi) sawal se bachta hai. farmaya : aur ahale-jahannam panch ( tarah ke log ( hain wo kamzor jiske paas ( burai se) rokney wali) aql iffat , haya , ghairat ( koi cheez nahi jo tum mein se ( burey kaamon mein dusron ke) peechhey lagney waley log hain ( yahan tak ke) ghar walon aur maal ke peechhey bhi nahi jatey (unki bhi parwaa nahi kartey (aur aisa khayanet karne wala jiska koi bhi mafaad chahey bahut maamooli ho, ( dusron ki nazron se) ojhal hota hai. to wo usmein ( zaroor ( khayanat karta hai. aur aisa shakhs jo subah-Shaam tumharey ahal aur ayaal aur maal ke barey main tumhen dhokaa deta hai. aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kanjoosii ya jhoot ka bhi zikr farmaya aur bad-neeyat bad-khalq aur Abu-Ghassan ne apni hadis mein ye zikr nahi kiya : aap kharch karein to an-qareeb aap par kharch kiya jaeyga."
7208,"Saeed ne Qatada se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur apni hadis mein ye bayan nahi kiya : har maal jo maine bandey ko diya, halal hai."
7209,"hamein Yahya-bin-Saeed ne dustwaai ( kapdey bechney ( waley Hisham se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Qatada ne Mutrif se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ayaaz-bin-himaar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khutba diya phir hadis bayan ki aur uske aakhir mein kaha : Yahya ne kaha : Shoba ne Qatada se riwayat kartey huey kaha : unhon ( Qatada ( ne kaha : maine is hadis mein (jo bayan hua wo khud ( Mutrif se suna."
7210,"Matar ne kaha : mujhey Qatada ne Mutarrif-bin-Abdullah-bin-Shikhkhir se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Hazrat ayaaz-bin-himaar (Raziallahu anhu) se jo qabila mujaashea' se they, riwayat ki, kaha : aik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khutba dene ke liye hamarey darmyan khadey huey aur farmaya : Allah Taala ne mujhey hukm diya hai. iske baad Qatada se Hisham ki hadis ke mutabiq hadis bayan ki aur is mein mazeed ye kaha : Allah Taala ne mujh par wahi ki hai ke tum sab tawaazeh (mehman nawazi) ikhtiyar karo yahan tak ke koi shakhs doosrey par fakhr na karey aur koi shakhs doosrey par zyadti na kare. unhon-ne is hadis mein kaha : wo tum mein) burai ke kaamon mein dusron ke) peechhey lagney waley hain. ghar-walon aur maal ke bhi khoji nahi (ke kamaa kar dusron se beniyaz ho jaaein.) to main ( Qatada ( ne ( Mutarrif se) kaha : abu Abdullah to ( ab ( yahi hua karega? unhon-ne kaha : haan , Allah ki qism ! maine jahiliyat ke zamaney mein unhein dekha ( aisa hota tha) ke aik shakhs poorey qabeeley ki bakriyan charaataa tha. usey unki aik kaneez ke siwa kuchh nahi milta tha jis se mujamiat (sambhog) karta tha."
7211,Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi shakhs faut hota hai to har subah aur Sham uska asl thikana uske samney laya jata hai. agar wo jannat walon mein se hai to ahle-jannat se aur agar wo dozakh walon mein se hai to dozakh mein se ( uska thikana usey dikhayaa jata hai aur us se) kaha jata hai. tumhara thikana hai. yahan tak ke Allah Taala qiyamat ke din tujhey zinda karke us ( thikaaney ( tak ley jaey.
7212,"Salim ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab koi shakhs faut hota hai to subah aur Sham uske samney uska thikana pesh kiya jata hai. agar wo ahle-jannat mein se ho to jannat aur agar ahale-dozakh mein se ho to dozakh (uske samney pesh ki jati hai) kaha : phir kaha jata hai ye tumhara wahi thikana hai jiski taraf qiyamat ke din tujhey dobara uthaakar ley jaya jaeyga."
7213,"ibne-Ulaih ne kaha : hamein Saeed Jurairi ne abu-Nazara se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, ( abu-Nazara ne) kaha : Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine ye hadis Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke roo-baroo hazir ho kar nahi suni , balke mujhey Hazrat Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik baar jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) banu-Najjaar ke aik baagh main apne khachchar par Sawar they, ham aap ke sath they ke achcha wo bidak gaya wo aapko giraaney laga tha ( dekha to ( wahan chh ya panch ya char qabrein thin ( ibne-Ulaih ne) kaha : Jurairi isi tarah kaha kartey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : in qabron walon ko kon janta hai? aik aadmi ne kaha : main, aap ne farmaya : ye log Kab marey they? usne kaha : shirk (ke aalam) mein marey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye log apni qabron mein mubtlaaey azab hain agar ye khadsha (dar) na hota ke tum (apne mardon ko) dafn na karogey to main Allah se dua karta ke qabr ke jis azab (ki aawaazon ( ko main sun raha hun wo tumhen bhi suna de. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamari taraf rukh anwar phera aur farmaya : aag ke azab se Allah ki panah maango. sab ne kaha ham aag ke azab se Allah ki panah mein aatey hain phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qabr ke azab se Allah ki panah maango. sab ne kaha : ham qabr ke azab se Allah ki panah mein aatey hain, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (tamam) fitnon se jo unmein se zahir hain aur jo posheeda hain Allah ki panah maango. sab ne kaha : ham fitnon se jo zahir hain aur posheeda hain Allah ki panah mein aatey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : dajjal ke fitney se Allah ki panah maango. sab ne kaha : ham dajjal ke fitney se Allah ki panah mein aatey hain."
7214,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar ye khadsha (dar) na hota ke tum ( mardon ko) dafn na karogey to main Allah Taala se dua karta ke wo tum ko azaabe-qabr (ki aawaazein ( sunwaaey.
7215,"Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat abu Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) suraj ghurub honey ke baad bahar tashrif le gaey aap ne aik awaz suni to farmaya : yahood hain unhein qabr mein azab diya ja raha hai."
7216,Sheban-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne Qatada se riwayat ki kaha : hamein Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki kaha : Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bandey ko jab uski qabr mein rakha jata hai aur us ke sathi usey chhodkar wapas jatey hain to wo ( banda ( unke jooton ki aahat sunta hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : uske paas do Farishtey aatey hain usko bithatey hain aur us se kehtey hain. tum us aadmi ke mutaalliq ( duniya mein) kya kaha kartey they? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jahan tak momin hai to wo kehta hai main gawahi deta hun ke wo Allah ke bandey aur uske rasool hain. farmaya : to us se kaha jaeyga tum dozakh main apne thikaaney ki taraf dekho Allah Taala ne iske badley tumhen jannat mein aik thikana de diya hai. Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo apne donon thikaanon ko aik sath dekhega . Qatada ne kaha : aur ham se ye bayan kiya gaya hai ke uski qabr mein sattar (70) hath wusat kar di jati hai aur qiyamat tak uski qabr mein taro taaza ne'matein bhar di jati hain.
7217,"Yazeed-bin-Zaree ne kaha : hamein Saeed-bin-abi-Aruba ne Qatada se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maiyyat ko jab qabr mein rakha jata hai to logon ke wapas jatey waqt wo unke jooton ki awaz sunta hai."
7218,"abdul-wahaab-bin-Ata ne Saeed (bin-abi-Aruba) se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab bandey ko qabr mein rakha jata hai aur uske sathi rukh mod kar chal padtey hain. iske baad Qatada se Sheban ki bayan ki hui riwayat ki tarah bayan kiya."
7219,Sad-bin-ubaida ne Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala imaan laney walon ko pukhta qaul (kalima taiba ki haqiqi shahadat (ke zariey se ( haq par) Sabit qadam rakhta hai. farmaya : ye aayat azaabe-qabr ke barey mein nazil hui us ( marney waale) se kaha ja ta hai. tumhara rab kon hai? wo ( momin ( kehta hai. mera rab Allah hai aur mere Nabi Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hain yahi qaul Shan wale Allah                                                          (يُثَبِّتُ اللَّهُ الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا بِالْقَوْلِ الثَّابِتِ فِي الْحَيَاةِ الدُّنْيَا وَفِي الْآخِرَةِ) (se murad ( hai.
7220,khaisma ne Hazrat baraa-bin-aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se (is aayat ke barey mein) riwayat ki : Allah Taala imaan laney walon ko duniya ki zindagi aur aakhirat mein pukhta qaul par Sabit qadam rakhta hai. kaha : ye aayat azaabe-qabr ke mutaalliq nazil hui hai.
7221,"mujhey Ubaidullah-bin-Umar qawaareeri ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Hammad-bin-Zaid ne hadis bayan ki unhon-ne kaha : hamein Budail ne Abdullah-bin-Shaqeeq se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : jab momin ki Rooh nikal jati hai to wo Farishtey us ( Rooh ( ko letey hain aur usey uper ki taraf ley jatey hain. Hammad ne kaha : unhon-ne uski khushbu ka zikr kiya aur kastoori ki baat ki. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aasman waley kehtey hain. ye aik pakeeza Rooh hai zamin walon ki taraf se aai hai) aey Rooh momin ! ( tujh par aur us jism par jisey to ne abad kiye rakha Allah ki rehmat ho. chunanche usey uske shan-waley rab ke paas ley jaya jata hai phir wo farmata hai. usey muqarrar shuda aakhiri muddat tak ke liye ( aali shaan thikaaney par) ley jao . farmaya : aur kaafir , jab uski Rooh nikalti hai. Hammad ne kaha : aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski badboo aur (is par ki janey wali) la'naton ka zikr kiya aur aasman waley kehtey hain. gandi Rooh hai zamin ki taraf se aai hai farmaya : to kaha jata hai usey muqarrar shuda aakhiri muddat tak ke liye ( burey thikaaney ( par ley jao . Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chadar jo aap ke jism Mubarak par thi is tarah mod kar apni naak par rakhi."
7222,"Sulaiman-bin-Mugheera ne kaha : hamein Sabit ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Makka aur Madina ke darmyan they, to ham ne pehli ka chaand dekhney ki koshish ki, main tez nazar insan tha maine chaand ko dekh liya. mere alawa aur koi nahi tha jiska khayal ho ke usne usey dekh liya hai. (hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : phir main Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se kehney laga : kya aap dekh nahi rahe? chunanche unhon-ne usey dekhnaa chhod diya, kaha : Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) keh rahe they an-qareeb main apne bistar par leta hunga to usey dekh loonga. phir unhon-ne ham se ahale-badr ka waqia bayan karna shuru kar diya. unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik din pahley hamein badr (main qatl honey) walon ke girney ki jaghein dikhaa rahe they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they : insha-Allah ! kal falan ke qatl honey ki jagah ye hogi. kaha : to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha is zaat ki qism jisne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko haq ke sath bheja ! wo log un jaghon ke kinaron se zara bhi idhar udhar (qatl) nahi huey they jinki nishaandehi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ki thi. (hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : phir un (ki laashon) ko aik doosrey ke uper kuwein mein daal diya gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chal kar unke paas pahunchey aur farmaya : aey falan-bin-falan aur aey falan-bin-falan ! kya tum ne Allah aur uske rasool se kiye huey waadey ko sachcha paya? bila shubah maine us waadey ko bilkul sachcha paya hai jo Allah ne mere sath kiya tha. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! aap un jismon se kaisey baat kar rahe hain jin mein roohein nahi hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main jo kuchh keh raha hun tum log usko unse zyada sunney waley nahi ho. magar wo meri baat ka koi jawab dene ki taqat nahi rakhtey."
7223,"Hammaad-bin-Salma ne Sabit Bunani se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teen din tak badr ke qatl huey logon ko padaa rehney diya. phir aap gaey aur unke paas khadey ho kar unko pukar kar farmaya : aey abu-Jahal-bin-Hisham ! aey Umayya-bin-Khalaf ! aey Utba-bin-Rabee ! aey Sheba-bin-Rabee ! kya tum ne wo wada sachcha nahi paya jo tumharey rab ne tum se kiya tha? maine to apne rab ke waadey ko sachcha paya hai. jo usney mere sath kiya tha ! Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ye irshad suna to arz kiya , Allah ke rasool ! ye log kaisey sunein gey aur kahan se jawab dengey, jabke wo to laashein bin chukey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! tum is baat ko jo main unse keh raha hun unki nisbat zyada sunney waley nahi ho. lekin wo jawab dene ki taqat nahi rakhtey. phir aap ne unke barey mein hukm diya to unhein ghaseetaa gaya aur badr ke kuwein mein daal diya gaya."
7224,"Abdul-Aala aur Rooh-bin-Ubada ne Saeed-bin-abi-Aruba se unhon-ne Qatada se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) se (sun kar) bayan kiya, unhon-ne kaha : jab badr ka din tha aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un par fateh hasil farmai to aap ne Quraish ke badey sardaaron mein se bees (20) afraad ke barey mein hukm diya aur Rooh (bin-Ubada) ki hadis mein hai ke chobis (24) afraad ke barey mein) hukm diyaa) to unhein badr ke pattharon se baney huey kuwon mein se aik kuwein mein daal diya gaya phir unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se Sabit ki riwayat ki hui hadis ke mutabiq hadis bayan ki."
7225,Ismail-bin-Ulaih ne Ayub se unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Ubai Muleka se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat ke din jis se hisab liya gaya wo azab mein mubtala ho gaya. maine arz ki. kya Allah Taala ne ye nahi farmaya : an-qareeb us se aasan hisab liya jaeyga? to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo hisab nahi wo to hisab ke liye pesh hona hai jis se qiyamat ke din hisab ki poochh gachh hui usey azab (mein daal ( diya jaeyga.
7226,Hammad-bin-Zaid ne kaha : hamein Ayub ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
7227,"abu-Yunus qushairi ne hamein hadis bayan ki kaha : hamein ibne-abi-Mulaika ne Qasim se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jiska bhi hisab kitab shuru ho gaya wo halaak ho gaya. maine arz ki, Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! kya Allah Taala ye nahi farmata : aasan hisab hoga? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo to hisab ke liye pesh hona hai lekin jis se muhaasbey mein poochh-gachh shuru ho gaee wo halaak ho jaeyga."
7228,"Usman-bin-Aswad ne ibne-abi-Mulaika se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis se hisab mein poochh-gachh shuru ho gaee wo halaak ho jaeyga phir abu-Yunus ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
7229,"Yahya-bin-Zakariya ne Aamash se, unhon-ne abu-Sufiyan se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aap ki wafat se teen din pahley ye farmatey huey suna : tum mein se har shakhs ko usi haalat mein maut aaey ke wo Allah ke mutaalliq achha guman rakhta ho."
7230,"Jareer, abu-Muawiya aur Esa-bin-Yunus ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
7231,"abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aap ki wafat se teen din pahley ye farmatey huey suna : tum mein se kisi par bhi maut na aaey magar us haalat mein ke wo izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ke mutaalliq achchha guman rakhta ho."
7232,"Jarir ne Aamash se, unhon-ne abu Sufiyan se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : har shakhs ko (iman aur ummeed ki) usi kaifiyat mein uthaya jaeyga jis par usko maut aai thi."
7233,"Sufiyan ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath , usi ki tarah riwayat ki aur kaha : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat hai aur ye nahi kaha : maine (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se) suna."
7234,"Hamza-bin-Abdullah-bin-Umar ne bataya ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : jab Allah Taala kisi qaum ko azab dene ka irada karta hai to har us shakhs par jo unmein tha, azab aata hai, iske baad wo apne apney aamal ke mutabiq uthaey jaengey."
